---
import Layout from '../../layouts/layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Forcepoint Security Solutions">

<main class="bg-gray-900 text-white min-h-screen">

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 py-24">

<div class="flex items-center gap-6">

<img src="/logos/forcepoint.png" class="h-12" alt="Forcepoint">

<div>

<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-blue-400">
Forcepoint
</h1>

<p class="text-gray-300 mt-2">
Human-centric cybersecurity focused on data protection, insider threat detection, and policy enforcement.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 pb-24 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2">

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Core Products
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Forcepoint DLP</li>
<li>• Forcepoint Insider Threat</li>
<li>• Web Security Gateway</li>
<li>• Cloud Access Security Broker (CASB)</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Capabilities
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Data loss prevention across cloud and on-prem</li>
<li>• Insider threat detection and analytics</li>
<li>• Policy-driven data protection</li>
<li>• Cloud and web security controls</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Use Cases
</h2>

<ul class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300 space-y-2">

<li>• Protecting intellectual property and sensitive data</li>
<li>• Monitoring insider risk and abnormal behavior</li>
<li>• Enforcing data policies in cloud applications</li>
<li>• Securing web traffic and remote work access</li>

</ul>

</div>

<div class="bg-gray-800 border border-gray-700 rounded-xl p-6">

<h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-300">
Why Forcepoint
</h2>

<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-gray-300">
Forcepoint combines user-aware data protection with cloud and web controls to prevent data loss while enabling business productivity.
</p>

</div>

</section>

</main>

</Layout>
